Package UI

package UI
  • Class
    Description
    BaseUI
    This abstract class serves as a base for creating UI components in the application.
    ButtonCreator
    This class provides a utility method to create clickable buttons with custom styling.
    DashboardUI
    This class represents the user interface for the dashboard.
    DishUI
    The `DishUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing dishes and their ingredients in the restaurant management system.
    GraphCreator
    This class is responsible for creating and managing line charts and bar charts.
    InventoryUI
    The `InventoryUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing ingredients in the restaurant management system.
    MainUI
    Main user interface for the application.
    MenusUI
    The `MenusUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing menus, dishes, and wines in the restaurant management system.
    SalesUI
    The `SalesUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing sales, generating sales reports, and viewing popular items in the restaurant management system.
    StaffUI
    The `StaffUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing staff schedule and holidays.
    StockOrdersUI
    The StockOrdersUI class represents the user interface for managing stock orders.
    TableOverviewUI
    The `TableOverviewUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing tables, table layouts, and table bookings in the restaurant management system.
    UISwitcher
    Interface to switch between different UI screens.
    WasteUI
    The `WasteUI` class extends the `BaseUI` class and represents the user interface for managing and displaying waste information in the restaurant management system.
    WineUI
    This class represents the user interface for managing wine data.
